тивном правонарушении в случае неисполнения уведомления.</p><p>Приложение: гарантийное письмо от Учреждения</p><p>Дата устранения: 01.11.2021 года.</p>","author_name":"Администрация Выборгского района","performer":null,"response_performers":[],"files":[{"id":17634432,"url":"/storage/2/2cfab12d-f4b8-425f-b877-29328eece88e.pdf","original_name":"Ответ на обращение подпись.pdf"}],"photos":[{"id":17634433,"url":"/storage/2/52a90930-a2e5-4957-b0af-ce5de9a5db6c.jpeg","original_name":"A164983B-74D3-473F-947C-753847F8DD62.jpeg","thumbnail":"/media/cache/34/bc/34bcc4f77633bd48800ee92feb295a43.jpg","size":"1280x720"}],"reject":null,"interim_date":"2021-11-01"},"meta":{"title":"Ответ","icon_text":"ПО","icon_title":"Промежуточный ответ","bg_color":"#E3F2FD","border_color":"#536DFE","status_font_color":"#FFFFFF","status_bg_color":"#A5D6A7","icon_bg_color":"#536DFE"},"content_type":28},{"widget":"public.status","key":"changestatus_12733189","payload":{"id":12733189,"dt":"2021-01-02T14:22:09.465310","status_name":"Рассмотрение","status":3},"meta":{"title":"Изменение статуса сообщения","bg_color":"#EEEEEE","icon":"fa-clock-o","icon_bg_color":"#FCAA62"},"content_type":30},{"widget":"public.status","key":"changestatus_12727938","payload":{"id":12727938,"dt":"2020-12-31T20:19:46.870205","status_name":"Модерация","status":1},"meta":{"title":"Изменение статуса сообщения","bg_color":"#EEEEEE","icon":"fa-hand-paper-o","icon_bg_color":"#469ED3"},"content_type":30},{"widget":"public.petition","key":"petition_3452680","payload":{"id":3452680,"dt":"2020-12-31T20:19:46.737487","status_name":"Промежуточный ответ","body":[{"text":"Ямы на въезде \nНужен срочный ремонт !","typeof":1}],"photos":[{"url":"/storage/1/6eb89723-e25c-4618-9e28-9b06841e226c.jpeg","original_name":"8366F2CD-550D-42B6-9A66-184D8BB9ECA9-6694-000003AEC5CA439C.jpeg","id":3924733,"thumbnail":"/media/cache/97/ae/97ae586b948282e0565c513e85fef42a.jpg","original_url":"/storage/1/6eb89723-e25c-4618-9e28-9b06841e226c.jpeg","size":"3024